!item [Name:]
ØReverse video onÆ - Switch on inverse video mode.

!item [Opcode:]
5 (Escape 13)

!item [Syntax:]
void v_rvon ( int16_t handle );

!item [Description:]
The call v_rvon activates the inverse alpha text display on the workstation
with the ID (!I)handle.(!i)

!item [(!nolink [Return]) value:]
The function does not return a result. 

!item [Availability:]
Supported by all screen drivers.

!item [Group:]
